{"tid":1773294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"到底除咗星火612，仲有邊度可以直接幫手足？","createTime":"2019-12-07T10:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T14:59:06.000Z","uid":219736,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e32dcb14db3c259beb8b1395647b53522810d164","tid":1773294,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">答案就係本士創作室</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知邊個係盧建民手足？佢就係初一義士，被判7年⋯呢個基金曾經幫助過佢患癌爸爸籌集捐款，直接幫到手足！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【首次呼籲各界友好 私募籌款支援抗爭】<br />\n<br />\n這幾年來不才 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joellaucl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoellaucl&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=129edbab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joellaucl</a> 以個人微弱的積蓄、法律界朋友和一群友好籌款直接支援過的抗爭義士不下數十，而幫過手或間接支援過的 (轉介、通報、義務咨詢等等) 更是多不勝數。支援的總金額累積已超過百萬元 (絕大多數是本人及友好的私下捐助)。另外上庭、探訪在囚義士及書寫法庭記錄的義務工作時間，已經不下兩千小時！當中還不計令《本土新聞》得以續命，日以繼夜不止息支援本土義士和抗爭文宣的努力。當中涉及要道謝的好友、義工及團體實在有太多，亦因私隱緣故暫且不表。<br />\n<br />\n近五個多月來「反送中」的各式支援和活動所花費的金錢和心力令人更是疲憊。由於反送中抗爭的局面不容樂觀，相信日後各方面的需要和付出只會越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n不才現特意在此呼籲，本人所處理半公開或非公開的支援活動已經出現財赤 (即是依靠本人及友好恆常的義捐及義助已經「乾塘」，持續運作和支援費用只能靠本人的額外預支)。若是 閣下 認同不才這五年來的支援和抗爭活動，請把義助款項存入本人以下的支票戶口 （恆生銀行 360-157465-001丨LAU CHI LAI 或 PAYME 68009934），以便不才持續提供資源幫助抗爭義士〔來年的目標支出約為五十至一百萬元〕。一如既往，所籌得的總數會以閣下自選的外號 (或以無名氏N) 公佈，再轉入《本土創作室》的非公開流水帳目，以便不時「非公開」地捐助真正有「財困」的義士和團體。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭和支援路上，每多的是人云亦云、跟紅頂白、錦上添花，明心見性、雪中送炭可有幾人？<br />\n<br />\n多說便俗，就止打住。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 是次朋友及網友的私募所得，會全數用作支援抗爭義士及活動。若想直接資助本土新聞，請去主頁 <a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=6ceeadfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.localpresshk.com</a> 底部看資助方法。<br />\n<br />\n近期實報實銷的兩次私募<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=809243102776464&amp;id=260980877602692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D809243102776464%26id%3D260980877602692&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=11d49525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=809243102776464&amp;id=260980877602692</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10218024176530339&amp;id=1063924497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10218024176530339%26id%3D1063924497&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=c2c0e78f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10218024176530339&amp;id=1063924497</a><br />\n<br />\n〔附圖是兩年前的舊帖，最終有幾萬元的進帳而全數已經用作義士支援〕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jf93amh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjf93amh.jpg&h=0d4d77d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook :  <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/StudioCreativeLocal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FStudioCreativeLocal%2F&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRCZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=9096c380\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/StudioCreativeLocal/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push !"},{"pid":"19d1812b25d6aadb16d7be40b9c6b3b51d415892","tid":1773294,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:56:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87e370893bb2427e60a189bdca73d2116ceb1b40","tid":1773294,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"128 維園見"},{"pid":"aae52007dfe7918f5657e3e750e8818131d04046","tid":1773294,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"128 維園見"},{"pid":"64648385186273497f89627ca1c60dc95fad8a01","tid":1773294,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re